get initial params

m <- 12
N <- nrow(dnpc)
Ns <-  as.integer(N/m+1)

  
#get yearly avg
savg <- vector()
for (j in 1:Ns) {
  savgsum <- 0.
  scount <- 0
  for (k in (m*(j-1)+1):(m*j)) {
    #print(c(j,m,k))
    if (k<=N){
      savgsum <- savgsum + yts[k] 
      scount <- scount + 1
      #print( c(j,k,savgsum,scount) )
    }
  }
  savg[j] <- savgsum/scount
}

#initial seasonality
#get avg diff from average for each period
s0 <- vector()
for (i in 1:m) {
  value <-  0
  vcount <-  0
  for (j in 1:Ns) {
    if ((m*(j-1)+i)<=N) {
      value <- value + yts[m*(j-1)+i]-savg[j]
      vcount <- vcount + 1
      #print( c(i,j,m*(j-1)+i,value,vcount) )
    }
  }
  s0[i] <-  value/vcount
}

yts_s1adj <-  ts(yts[1:12]-s0, start=c(2011,1), frequency=12)
yts_etsadj <- ts(yts[1:12]-s1ets, start=c(2011,1), frequency=12)
yts_mean1 <- ts(rep(mean(yts[1:12]),times=12), start=c(2011,1), frequency=12) 

dygraph(cbind(yts[1:12],yts_s1adj,yts_etsadj,yts_mean1)) #should this be flatter?

b0 <- summary(initreg)$coefficients['x','Estimate']

make function to smooth data, if components=TRUE, will return components instead of model

modelAAA <- function(y,alpha,betastar,gamma,l0,b0,s0,components=FALSE) {
  m <- 12
  N <- length(y)
  Ns <-  as.integer(N/m+1)
  
  smoothy <- vector()
  l <- vector()
  b <- vector()
  s <- vector()
  
  smoothy[1] <- l0+b0+s0[1]
  l[1] <-  alpha*(y[1]-s0[1]) + (1-alpha)*(l0+b0)
  b[1] <-  betastar*(l[1]-l0) + (1-betastar)*b0
  s[1] <-  gamma*(y[1]-l0-b0) + (1-gamma)*s0[1]

  for (t in 2:12) {
    l[t] <- alpha*(y[t]-s0[t]) + (1-alpha)*(l[t-1] + b[t-1])
    b[t] <- betastar*(l[t]-l[t-1]) + (1-betastar)*b[t-1]
    s[t] <- gamma*(y[t]-l[t-1]-b[t-1]) + (1-gamma)*s0[t]
    smoothy[t] <- l[t]+b[t]+s0[t]
  }
  
  for (t in 13:N) {
    l[t] <- alpha*(y[t]-s[t-m]) + (1-alpha)*(l[t-1] + b[t-1])
    b[t] <- betastar*(l[t]-l[t-1]) + (1-betastar)*b[t-1]
    s[t] <- gamma*(y[t]-l[t-1]-b[t-1]) + (1-gamma)*s[t-m]
    smoothy[t] <- l[t]+b[t]+s[t-m]
  }
  if (!components) {return(smoothy)}
  if (components) {return(list(l=l,b=b,s=s))}

}

RMSE <- function(actual, predicted){
  sqrt(mean((actual - predicted)^2))
}

test out function

stanaaa <- modelAAA(yts,alpha,betastar,gamma,l0,b0,s0)
etsaaa <- modelAAA(yts,alphaets,betaets/alphaets,gammaets,l1ets,b1ets,s1ets)
dygraph(cbind(yts,stants,stanaaa,yets,etsaaa))
rmsestan <- RMSE(yts,stanaaa)
rmseets <- RMSE(yts,etsaaa)
print(c(rmsestan,rmseets))
## [1] 0.7864064 1.1402944
